                "text": {
                  "status": "generated",
                  "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h2>4.1 Therapeutic indications</h2><p>Joenja is indicated for the treatment of activated phosphoinositide 3‑kinase delta syndrome (APDS) in adults and adolescents 12 years of age and older.</p></div></div>"
