                  "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h2>4.3 Contraindications</h2><p>Hypersensitivity to the active substance or to any of the excipients listed in section 6.1.</p></div></div>"
