                "text": {
                  "status": "generated",
                  "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h2>4.7 Effects on ability to drive and use machines</h2><p>Joenja has no or negligible influence on the ability to drive and use machines.</p></div></div>"
