                "text": {
                  "status": "generated",
                  "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h2>4.9 Overdose</h2><p>If overdose occurs, the patient must be monitored for evidence of toxicity (see section 4.8). Treatment of overdose with Joenja consists of general supportive measures including monitoring of vital signs as well as observation of the clinical status of the patient.</p></div></div>"
